net.sf.hajdbc.balancer

Class AbstractBalancer<Z,D extends Database<Z>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.hajdbc.balancer.AbstractBalancer<Z,D>
  • Type Parameters:
    Z -
    D -
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<D>, Collection<D>, Set<D>, Balancer<Z,D>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractSetBalancer, LoadBalancer

    public abstract class AbstractBalancer<Z,D extends Database<Z>>
extends Object
implements Balancer<Z,D>
    Thread-safe abstract balancer implementation that implements most of the Balancer interface, except Balancer.next(). Uses A copy-on-write algorithm for Set.add(Object), Set.remove(Object), and Set.clear(). Calls to iterator() are non-blocking.
    Author:
    Paul Ferraro
